snippet.title: TMZLive
snippet.description: Step inside the TMZ newsroom for an hour a day to see how news is made. TMZ Live blends elements of the TMZ website with TV for a global conversation that starts in the newsroom and involves viewers from all over the world via skype, phone and twitter.  Join Harvey Levin, Charles Latibeaudiere and the rest of the TMZ staff as hot topics and breaking news are argued.  Celebrities come in to talk about breaking stories, especially those in which they are involved.
